---
/**
 * Favicons.astro
 *
 * This component renders favicon link tags for various device types and formats.
 * It provides comprehensive favicon support including traditional ICO files,
 * modern SVG favicons, Apple touch icons, and maskable icons for PWA support.
 *
 * Features:
 * - Multiple favicon formats for cross-browser compatibility
 * - Apple touch icon for iOS home screen bookmarks
 * - SVG favicon with maskable support for modern browsers
 * - Properly sized assets for different device requirements
 *
 * Asset Imports:
 * - favIcon: Traditional ICO format favicon (16x16, 32x32)
 * - favIconSvg: SVG format favicon for scalable graphics
 * - appleTouchIcon: High-resolution PNG for Apple touch devices (180x180)
 *
 * Favicon Types:
 * - rel="shortcut icon": Legacy ICO format for broad compatibility
 * - rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml": Modern SVG favicon support
 * - rel="mask-icon": SVG mask for Safari pinned tabs
 * - rel="apple-touch-icon": iOS home screen icon
 *
 * Data Flow:
 * 1. Imports favicon assets from assets/favicons directory
 * 2. Renders link tags with appropriate rel, type, and sizes attributes
 * 3. Provides comprehensive favicon coverage for different browsers/devices
 *
 * Usage Context:
 * - Included in BaseLayout for site-wide favicon support
 * - Renders in document head for early favicon loading
 * - Supports both traditional and modern favicon formats
 *
 * Asset Requirements:
 * - favicon.ico: Multi-size ICO file (16x16, 32x32)
 * - favicon.svg: Scalable vector graphic
 * - apple-touch-icon.png: 180x180 PNG for iOS devices
 *
 * Browser Support:
 * - ICO: All browsers (legacy support)
 * - SVG: Modern browsers (Chrome 90+, Firefox 92+)
 * - Apple Touch: iOS Safari
 * - Mask Icon: Safari pinned tabs
 */
---

{
  /*
    Traditional favicon.ico for broad browser compatibility.
    - Uses static file from /favicons/favicon.ico
    - rel="shortcut icon" for legacy browser support
  */
}
<link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicons/favicon.ico" />

{
  /*
    SVG favicon for modern browsers with scalable graphics support.
    - Uses static file from /favicons/favicon.svg
    - type="image/svg+xml" for proper MIME type
    - Provides crisp icons at any resolution
  */
}
<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicons/favicon.svg" />

{
  /*
    Maskable SVG icon for Safari pinned tabs.
    - Uses static file from /favicons/favicon.svg
    - color attribute sets the mask color (#8D46E7 - theme purple)
    - Provides monochrome icon for Safari's pinned tab feature
  */
}
<link rel="mask-icon" href="/favicons/favicon.svg" color="#8D46E7" />

{
  /*
    Apple touch icon for iOS home screen bookmarks.
    - Uses static file from /favicons/apple-touch-icon.png (180x180)
    - sizes attribute specifies icon dimensions
    - Provides high-resolution icon for Apple devices
  */
}
<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/favicons/apple-touch-icon.png" />
